<SYNC Start=1085084><P Class=KRCC>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=1086186><P Class=KRCC>
잠시만 기다려보게
<SYNC Start=1088120><P Class=KRCC>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=1092026><P Class=KRCC>
