<SYNC Start=1446008><P Class=KRCC>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=1447147><P Class=KRCC>
따지지 말게, 벤저
<SYNC Start=1449115><P Class=KRCC>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=1450250><P Class=KRCC>
