<SYNC Start=1521116><P Class=KRCC>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=1523957><P Class=KRCC>
- 지방판이요? 전국판요?<br>
- 지방판으로요
<SYNC Start=1526357><P Class=KRCC>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=1531732><P Class=KRCC>
불을 꺼
<SYNC Start=1534496><P Class=KRCC>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=1551118><P Class=KRCC>
